<Layout active="real-estate" title="Real Estate Division | Legion Services LLC" description="Real estate sales through Cornerstone Realty plus staging, photography, and drone mapping services." contactPhone="(304) 590-1434" contactPhoneHref="+13045901434" contactEmail="brandonjfhickman@gmail.com">
<section class="page-hero"><div class="wrap page-hero-inner"><div><div class="eyebrow">Legion Services LLC</div><h1>Real Estate Division</h1><h2>Local expertise. Professional presentation.</h2><p>Real estate sales, property marketing, staging, photography, and drone mapping—combined to help clients prepare, position, and move property with confidence.</p><div class="actions"><a class="btn" href="tel:+13045901434">Call (304) 590-1434</a><a class="btn outline" href="mailto:brandonjfhickman@gmail.com?subject=Real%20Estate%20Inquiry">Email Brandon</a><a class="btn outline" href="https://www.cornerstonerealtywv.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Cornerstone Realty</a></div></div><div class="hero-art">⌂</div></div></section>
<section class="section"><div class="wrap"><div class="section-head"><div class="eyebrow">Real Estate Services</div><h2>More than a listing.</h2><p>Sales representation is paired with practical property services that help a home, building, or parcel present at its best.</p></div><div class="services">{services.map(([i,t,d])=><article class="service"><div class="icon">{i}</div><h3>{t}</h3><p>{d}</p></article>)}</div></div></section>
<section class="section dark-band"><div class="wrap portrait-panel"><img src="/assets/brandon-hickman.png" alt="Brandon J. F. Hickman, West Virginia real estate salesperson" /><div class="portrait-copy"><div class="eyebrow">Local expertise. Trusted partnership.</div><h2>Brandon J. F. Hickman</h2><p><strong>Salesperson/REALTOR®</strong></p><p>Brandon provides real estate sales services through Cornerstone Realty, LLC under the supervision of Jan Hoover, Broker. The Legion Services Real Estate Division also provides separate support services such as staging, photography, and drone mapping.</p><div class="cornerstone-mark">Cornerstone Realty</div><p><a class="btn" href="https://www.cornerstonerealtywv.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Cornerstone Realty ↗</a></p><div class="disclosure"><strong>Real Estate Advertising Disclosure:</strong> Real estate brokerage services are offered through Cornerstone Realty, LLC. Brandon J. F. Hickman is identified as a West Virginia Salesperson/REALTOR® and is brokered by Jan Hoover, Broker. Cornerstone Realty, LLC, Jan Hoover, Broker, 3568 Teays Valley Road, Suite 200, Hurricane, WV 25526, (304) 757-0889. Legion Services LLC is not a real estate brokerage. Equal Housing Opportunity. Brokerage identification and final advertising format should be approved by the responsible broker before publication.</div></div></div></section>
<section class="section"><div class="wrap split"><div><div class="eyebrow">Property Marketing Support</div><h2>Prepare. Present. Perform.</h2><p>From room preparation and professional imagery to aerial mapping and land documentation, Legion Services can help create a more complete property-marketing package.</p></div><div class="stat-panel"><div class="stat">Residential sales</div><div class="stat">Property staging</div><div class="stat">Photography</div><div class="stat">Drone mapping</div></div></div></section>
<section class="contact-band"><div class="wrap"><div><b style="font-size:24px">Ready to make your next move?</b><br />Call <a href="tel:+13045901434">(304) 590-1434</a> or email <a href="mailto:brandonjfhickman@gmail.com">brandonjfhickman@gmail.com</a>.</div><div class="actions"><a class="btn outline" href="tel:+13045901434">Call Brandon</a><a class="btn outline" href="mailto:brandonjfhickman@gmail.com?subject=Real%20Estate%20Inquiry">Email Brandon</a></div></div></section>
</Layout>
